---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About â€” River Roots Studio" description="Meet Donna, the guide behind River Roots Studio. Wanderer, wisdom seeker, risk taker, and lover of joy.">
  <!-- PAGE HEADER -->
  <section class="relative bg-moss/10 py-12 sm:py-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h1 class="font-heading text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-moss mb-3 leading-tight">
        A Glimpse of Me
      </h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PHOTO + BIO -->
  <section class="py-10 sm:py-12 lg:py-14">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 md:gap-12 items-start">
        <!-- Photo -->
        <div class="w-full md:w-2/5 flex-shrink-0">
          <img
            src="/images/donna-2.jpg"
            alt="Donna smiling warmly, surrounded by the creative materials she loves"
            class="w-full rounded-lg shadow-lg"
          />
        </div>

        <!-- Bio -->
        <div class="space-y-5 text-brown/80 text-lg leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            <strong class="text-moss font-semibold font-heading">As a wanderer&hellip;</strong>
            I did 12-step work for 20 years.
          </p>
          <p>
            <strong class="text-moss font-semibold font-heading">As a wisdom seeker&hellip;</strong>
            I studied Spiritual Direction with Benedictine Nuns in Colorado.
          </p>
          <p>
            <strong class="text-moss font-semibold font-heading">As a risk taker&hellip;</strong>
            I followed the amazing Martha Beck into life coach training.
          </p>
          <p>
            <strong class="text-moss font-semibold font-heading">As a lover of joy&hellip;</strong>
            I became an Expressive Arts Coach with the multi-talented Lucia Capacchione.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CLOSING PARAGRAPH -->
  <section class="py-10 sm:py-12 bg-moss/5">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <p class="text-brown/80 text-lg sm:text-xl leading-relaxed text-center">
        I am a Grandmother of four wildlings, and a lover of nature, books, and hard truths. I create
        spaces that are filled with tenderness, beauty, and even a little humor. I&rsquo;ve been down
        long roads and I&rsquo;m here to offer some shelter for you from yours.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- RUMI QUOTE -->
  <section class="py-10 sm:py-12">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <blockquote>
        <svg class="w-8 h-8 mx-auto mb-4 text-terracotta/40" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
          <path d="M4.583 17.321C3.553 16.227 3 15 3 13.011c0-3.5 2.457-6.637 6.03-8.188l.893 1.378c-3.335 1.804-3.987 4.145-4.247 5.621.537-.278 1.24-.375 1.929-.311 1.804.167 3.226 1.648 3.226 3.489a3.5 3.5 0 01-3.5 3.5c-1.073 0-2.099-.49-2.748-1.179zm10 0C13.553 16.227 13 15 13 13.011c0-3.5 2.457-6.637 6.03-8.188l.893 1.378c-3.335 1.804-3.987 4.145-4.247 5.621.537-.278 1.24-.375 1.929-.311 1.804.167 3.226 1.648 3.226 3.489a3.5 3.5 0 01-3.5 3.5c-1.073 0-2.099-.49-2.748-1.179z" />
        </svg>
        <p class="font-heading text-xl sm:text-2xl lg:text-3xl text-brown italic leading-relaxed mb-3">
          I have been a seeker and I still am, but I&rsquo;ve stopped asking the books and the stars
          and started listening to the teaching of my own soul.
        </p>
        <footer class="text-brown/60">
          <cite class="not-italic text-sm">&mdash; Rumi</cite>
        </footer>
      </blockquote>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- TAGLINE + CTA -->
  <section class="py-10 sm:py-12 bg-moss/5">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <p class="font-heading text-xl sm:text-2xl text-terracotta italic mb-8">
        Expressive Arts is an archaeologist for your Inner Knowing.
      </p>
      <a
        href="/workshops"
        class="inline-block bg-terracotta hover:bg-terracotta-dark text-cream px-8 py-3 rounded-md font-medium text-lg transition-colors focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-terracotta focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-offset-cream"
      >
        Ready to explore? &rarr; See Workshops
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
